                         Encoder/Ripper: SMiLE                         
                                                                        
   READNFO is for the same reason as the others, the first 31 minutes   
   of the video is pretty blurry, after that it actually turns into     
   a very good CAM. Screenshots are included, with both blurry and      
   normal snapshots. We just did our usual with this: Dropped it into   
   conversion and then added our own mix of filters before then         
   running our custom encode settings over it. Turned out very nice     
   for a 525mb file. LiNE audio is pretty good, hardly any background   
   noise. If you can put up with the blurry segment then you will       
   enjoy this. Best quality for size on the net. Enjoy! 
